Class Summary
BingKM A KnowledgeMiner that deploys the Bing search engine to search the Web.
GoogleKM A KnowledgeMiner that deploys the Google search engine to search the Web.

IndriKM A KnowledgeMiner that deploys the Indri IR system to search a local text corpus.

KnowledgeMiner A KnowledgeMiner deploys a document retrieval system to search an unstructured knowledge source, e.g.
Searcher A Searcher queries an unstructured or (semi)structured knowledge source and passes the results to the static class Search.
WikipediaKA A KnowledgeAnnotator for the Wikipedia online encyclopedia.
WorldFactbookKA A KnowledgeAnnotator for the CIA World Factbook.
YahooKM A KnowledgeMiner that deploys the Yahoo search engine to search the Web.
